{"tid":1296463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大把貨] 網民發起「食窮民建聯」 蔣麗芸：大門係開嘅 歡迎班後生仔支持","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T23:48:23.000Z","uid":224066,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5634ec788a0d3aab7b1164a0595b1b2158e0a920","tid":1296463,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190707/_2019070709313176122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190707%2F_2019070709313176122.jpg&h=d3c2ed43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂雖暫緩，網民繼續有搞作，在「連登」發起「積極參與民建聯所有活動」行動，揚言「令到民建聯可以有一番新景象」，唔再係老人家先去參加佢哋活動。帖文一出，網民即不斷留言就自己所在地區的民建聯所搞活動「報料」，有人話要「食窮民建聯」。另有網民在其他社交網站開專頁，列出民建聯在各區的優惠活動，好似每位二百七十蚊參加會慶聚餐、又有平價電影戲飛同蚊怕水等。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯議員Ann姐蔣麗芸就同Kelly講無有怕，好歡迎佢哋參加，<span style=\"color: red;\">「可能啲後生仔得閒無嘢做」</span>，唔需要咁緊張！不過會慶聚餐一早已經賣晒飛，如果網民咁有興趣，可以睇吓其他途徑會唔會有剩飛賣。問到會不會擔心屆時出岔子？她話班後生仔要抗議的對象唔係街坊，相信唔會喺嗰啲場合搞事，而且都無得擔心，「唔通佢戴口罩，着黑衫就唔俾佢入場咩？」她又透露，嚟緊自己區都會搞啲包場睇電影活動，歡迎班後生仔買飛支持，「民建聯大門係開嘅！」"},{"pid":"9cfaa123d3bf7852285d0de4d0de08995e73ff74","tid":1296463,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"和理貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食撚窮你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0b0831aaf90afce4ddc06f6522bb74147416f5","tid":1296463,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"去影下證件相先"},{"pid":"7588a2dd77fcd83fe8a5b73ba31577e5fce01f72","tid":1296463,"uid":262695,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5wCuzCU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5wCuzCU.png&h=13eba043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哈"},{"pid":"d1e51213e205081687767a21822c27c3fdf150f4","tid":1296463,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"個個星期又沐浴露又2kg米,可以減少支出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bc9e41c5d475edd7f30a7ba6d5acd632d8cbe2","tid":1296463,"uid":222524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"元秋係咪同李慧琼鬥緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620ac35567904fa508802db3c80a5e3f45596dac","tid":1296463,"uid":258718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:52:06.000Z","msg":"和理食窮你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23dce386df1d78ef83edf9a0da756d295f0ef22d","tid":1296463,"uid":192968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:48:23.000Z","msg":"今日麥記派炸雞.....好多人拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}